Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:59.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「君が許さなかった世界はこんなにも綺麗だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:05.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「悲しみを生むこと、全てが悪だとでも言うのか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現実の銃口　突きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矜持たちが　壊れても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僕は僕でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:20.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Against the gunpoint, ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll rise like the break dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I save them for the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:29.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dream of the world for me and "fantasia"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's time to go...Unshaken mind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揺れる視界を薙ぎ払い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛すべき"正義"を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:53.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}語られない明日のために生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儚さと　痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}狂気だけが走らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全てが還る日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:06.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I face out, hold out to world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:59.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「你所不原谅的世界是这样美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:05.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「制造悲伤的一切都是邪恶吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现实的枪口已指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使矜持悉数破碎崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也仍然只是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:20.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迎着枪口 随时准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会像破晓的黎明那样喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为末日将他们拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:29.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向往着为我与幻想而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时候启程了…怀着坚定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}清空动摇的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找值得热爱的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:53.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为无从诉说的明天而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在虚幻与痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有疯狂在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一切回归之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:06.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我将勇敢地面对世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:37.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}理想なんて幻想って時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:46.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}貴方は何処へ手を伸ばすの…たった一人で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:53.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}Always...All ways...You stand by Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:21:01.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}何を護るために苦しんでいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:08.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}捕われてるままじゃ抱きしめられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:15.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}標識の無い道で泣いているChild
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:23.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}理想なんて玩具だって知って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:31.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}それでも…その手を差し伸ばしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}きっと正義の見方なんて手の先の視線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:50.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}構わないよ、見ていたいだけ…たった一人を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:37.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}在这理想不过是幻想的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:46.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你要孤身一人 将手伸向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:53.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你永远 由始至终 都与正义为邻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:21:01.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}你是为了保护什么而如此痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:08.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}身陷囹圄就无法拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:15.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}孩子 在没有道标的路上哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:23.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}即便知道理想只是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:31.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}也仍然伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}对正义的见解一定只取决于视线的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:50.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}那样也无所谓 我只想要看着那唯一的人
